            {
               "text": "### Introduction\n\nWhen studying the history of the Babylonian Diagonal Triple (Pythagorean Theorem) in the first text of this series, we were presented with a graph showing squares of visible sizes (<htcite0>; <htcite1>; <htcite2>):",
