t-weight=\"bold\" transform=\"rotate(53, 236, 0)\">25</text><text x=\"240\" y=\"186\" font-size=\"1.0em\" font-weight=\"bold\">θ</text></svg></p><p class=\"desc\"><b>Graph 1</b>: Visual proof of the Babylonian Diagonal Triple (Pythagorean Theorem).</p>",
               "source": [],
