               "text": "<div class=\"card\"><div class=\"triangle-visual\"><canvas id=\"triangleCanvas\" width=\"500\" height=\"340\" style=\"width:100%; height:auto; max-width:500px; aspect-ratio:500/340\"></canvas></div><div class=\"controls\"><div class=\"side-card leg-a\"><label>Leg a</label><input type=\"number\" id=\"sideAInput\" step=\"0.01\" min=\"0.5\" max=\"10\" value=\"3.00\"><div class=\"range-slider\"><input type=\"range\" id=\"sideARange\" min=\"1\" max=\"10\" step=\"0.01\" value=\"3\"></div></div><div class=\"side-card leg-b\"><label>Leg b</label><input type=\"number\" id=\"sideBInput\" step=\"0.01\" min=\"0.5\" max=\"10\" value=\"4.00\"><div class=\"range-slider\"><input type=\"range\" id=\"sideBRange\" min=\"1\" max=\"10\" step=\"0.01\" value=\"4\"></div></div><div class=\"side-card hyp-c\"><label>Hypotenuse c</label><input type=\"number\" id=\"sideCInput\" step=\"0.01\" min=\"1\" max=\"14.15\" value=\"5.00\"><div class=\"range-slider\"><input type=\"range\" id=\"sideCRange\" min=\"1\" max=\"14.15\" step=\"0.01\" value=\"5\"></div></div></div><div class=\"theorem-box\"><p>✨ <strong>Babylonian Diagonal Triple (Pythagorean Theorem)</strong> ✨</p><p class=\"equation\" id=\"theoremText\">a² + b² = c²</p><p id=\"numericProof\" style=\"font-size:0.8rem; opacity:0.85;\">3.00² + 4.00² = 5.00²  → 9.00 + 16.00 = 25.00</p></div></div>",
